metadata.name: Collectooor #1
metadata.description: A collection of 100 Collectooor NFTs brought to you by Index Coop. Collectooors are the ones who successfully pushed through to the meta layer of 'collectorism'. The OGs who bought into blue chip NFTs before the hype. A collective of like-minded individuals who care about true innovation and the beauty of technological and artistic evolution through NFTs. Art by cafpunk.
